[img/gradsky-1981.jpg]

# info
LP Сама жизнь
Александр Градский и группа “Скоморохи”
http://www.discogs.com/master/321388
Melodiya 1984 LP C60 21435 000
Recorded 1981

It's a vocal suite composed on lyrics of Paul Eluard. A good album and I like the lyrics too, but there is even a cool semi-progrock/semi-electronica instrumental thing on it entitled just as two bang signs. Notorious Vladimir Vasilkov (Владимир Васильков) plays drums here.

[alexander gradsky - bang bang 1981.mp3] A4 

